message.entry: Command argument must be either a nonmissing scalar string or a character row vector.
Environment variable names must be nonmissing scalar strings or character row vectors.
Environment variable values must be either scalar strings, scalar missing type values, or character row vectors.
Environment names must be a string array, cell array of character vectors, or character array.
Environment values must be a string array, cell array of character vectors, or character array.
Environment variable names must be nonmissing.
The array of environment values must have the same number of elements as the array of environment names or be scalar.
Environment names in a dictionary must be in a string array or cell array of character vectors.
Environment values in a dictionary must be in a string array or cell array of character vectors.
